! Gray-Code Golden-Spiral Fold

A deterministic fold codec using Gray-code addresses and golden-spiral chart
positions for navigable ENE storage.

!! Why It Matters

It gives the wiki and graph layers a concrete geometry for addressable concept
retrieval instead of an unbounded keyword pile.

